 CONTENTS
 ========
 README -- this file
 Makefile.PL -- Perl Makefile template
 Filter.pm -- The Pod::Filter module source
 podfilter.PL -- A script to print selected sections of pod docs
                 in raw pod format


 REQUIREMENTS
 ============
 * Perl version 5.002 or later

 * Getopt::Long version 2.13 or later (podfilter.PL only)

 * Pod::PlainText version 0.01 or later (podfilter.PL only)

 * Pod::Usage version 0.01 or later (podfilter.PL only)


 BUILDING & INSTALLING
 =====================
 Please see the perl "ExtUtils::MakeMaker" manpage for how to build and
 install using the Makefile.PL template. In a nutshell, simply typing:

      perl Makefile.PL

 should build a Makefile with the usual targets like "all", "clean",
 "test", and "install".

